BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 181.68 750 Td (WHAT IS A VISION BOARD & WHY IT WORKS) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 738 m 552 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (A vision board is a visual representation of your goals, dreams,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (and the life you want to create. It works because:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (THE SCIENCE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (- Reticular Activating System \(RAS\): Your brain filters millions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (  of data points daily. When you focus on something visually,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (  your RAS starts noticing opportunities aligned with those goals.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (- Visualization activates the same brain regions as actual) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td (  experience, building neural pathways toward your goals.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (- Written goals are 42% more likely to be achieved.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (HOW TO USE THIS WORKBOOK:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (1. Assess where you are NOW in each life area \(honestly\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (2. Dream about where you WANT to be \(no limits!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (3. Set specific goals with action steps) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (4. Create your physical vision board \(images + words\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (5. Review daily, take action monthly, adjust quarterly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td (SUPPLIES FOR YOUR VISION BOARD:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td (- Poster board or cork board) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (- Magazines, printed images, quotes) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (- Scissors, glue, tape, markers) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td (- Stickers, washi tape \(optional\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (- A photo of yourself \(put it in the center!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 315 Td (Place it where you'll see it DAILY.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
